      "source": "JR北海道",
      "translation": "JR Hokkaido"
    },
    {
      "key": "contribution.{FBEAD293-1069-11D7-AA41-000740323A8D}.type",
      "source": "キハ40形",
      "translation": "Kiha 40 series"
    },
    {
      "key": "contribution.{FBEAD293-1069-11D7-AA41-000740323A8D}.description",
      "source": "老朽車両置き換えのため昭和５２年に登場した近郊形気動車。",
      "translation": "Suburban diesel railcar introduced in Showa 52 (1977) to replace aging rolling stock."
    },
