    {
      "key": "contribution.{15ED3147-F3A2-4C96-A620-54CD0A6EF500}.name",
      "source": "宗谷、サロベツ",
      "translation": "Sōya, Sarobetsu"
    },
    {
      "key": "contribution.{15ED3147-F3A2-4C96-A620-54CD0A6EF500}.company",
      "source": "JR北海道",
      "translation": "JR Hokkaido"
    },
    {
      "key": "contribution.{15ED3147-F3A2-4C96-A620-54CD0A6EF500}.type",
      "source": "キハ400形",
      "translation": "Kiha 400 Series"
    },
    {
      "key": "contribution.{15ED3147-F3A2-4C96-A620-54CD0A6EF500}.description",
      "source": "宗谷線の急行用にキハ40形を改造した形式。\n「宗谷」「サロベツ」「利尻」に使用されていたが、すべて特急に格上げされ、\nその際この形式での運転も終了した。",
      "translation": "A model modified from the Kiha 40 Series for express services on the Sōya Line. It was used for 'Sōya', 'Sarobetsu', and 'Rishiri' services, but all were upgraded to limited express, and operation with this model ceased at that time."
    },
    {
      "key": "contribution.{15ED3147-F3A2-4C96-A620-54CD0A6EF501}.name",
      "source": "盛岡色（ワンマン対応）",
      "translation": "Morioka color (one-man operation compatible)"
    },
    {
      "key": "contribution.{15ED3147-F3A2-4C96-A620-54CD0A6EF501}.company",
      "source": "JR東日本",
      "translation": "JR East"
    },
    {
      "key": "contribution.{15ED3147-F3A2-4C96-A620-54CD0A6EF501}.type",
      "source": "キハ40形",
      "translation": "Kiha 40 series"
    },
    {
      "key": "contribution.{15ED3147-F3A2-4C96-A620-54CD0A6EF501}.description",
      "source": "ワンマン対応車両の盛岡色です。「赤鬼」と呼ばれています。",
      "translation": "This is a Morioka-colored vehicle compatible with one-man operation. It is nicknamed 'Red Oni'."
