    {
      "key": "contribution.{ADF87135-9F9C-051A-9B45-04F846A0479D}.description",
      "source": "ドイツの技術を採用し100%低床化を実現した、超低床路面電車。\n特殊な構造の他にも、車内外のデザインや、市民グループが大きく関った導入経緯も、この車両の特徴である。\n公募により「MOMO」の愛称が付けられた。\n（実車の姿にするには2両に設定してください）",
      "translation": "An ultra-low-floor tram that achieved 100% low-floor design using German technology. In addition to its special structure, the interior and exterior design and the involvement of citizen groups in its introduction are also characteristics of this vehicle. It was given the nickname 'MOMO' through public solicitation. (Set to 2 cars to match the actual vehicle's appearance)"
    },
