      "key": "contribution.{BDEFADEA-5581-8000-75CF-885D7EDE8000}.description",
      "source": "平成5年、軌道線の非冷房車を置き換えるため5両新造された、VVVFインバータ制御車両。",
      "translation": "In 1993, 5 new VVVF inverter controlled cars were built to replace non-air-conditioned cars on the tram line."
    },
