      "translation": "205 Series"
    },
    {
      "key": "contribution.{002D31EE-F3A2-4CD6-A820-542DEA6E6537}.description",
      "source": "製造費を抑えつつ省エネルギー化を目指した通勤型電車。ステンレス車体やボルスタレス台車の採用により軽量化が図られている。",
      "translation": "Commuter electric train designed for energy saving while suppressing manufacturing costs. Lightweighting achieved through the adoption of stainless steel car bodies and bolsterless bogies."
    },
    {
      "key": "contribution.{003D31EE-F3A2-4CD6-A820-542DEA6E6537}.name",
