      "translation": "201 Series"
    },
    {
      "key": "contribution.{003D31EE-F3A2-4CD6-A820-542DEA6E6537}.description",
      "source": "103系の後継車両として開発された通勤型電車。様々な新機軸が積極的に取り入れられ、大幅な省エネルギー化が図られたが、その結果、製造コストが高くつくことになった。",
      "translation": "A commuter electric train developed as a successor to the 103 Series. Various new features were actively incorporated, achieving significant energy savings, but as a result, manufacturing costs became high."
    },
